summary: Dear Dr. Metcalf, our class hamster, Sprinkles, was replaced with a rabbit the other week. Our teacher told us to continue...
question: Dear Dr. Metcalf, our class hamster, Sprinkles, was replaced with a rabbit the other week. Our teacher told us to continue referring to him as Mr. Sprinkles. 2 days later, he was a snake, and yesterday, he was three mice. Mr. Terlingwhoosh is pretending like nothing is different, but everyone else in class can tell it's different animals. We're starting to freak out. Why are you doing this? -Billy Gobhoblin, 7th grade
answer: I assure you it’s the same animal, good ol’ Mr. Sprinkles.

summary: The Andi Mack Kids As The Last 7 Songs I Listened To On YouTube
title: The Andi Mack Kids As The Last 7 Songs I Listened To On YouTube
body:
The kids I’ll be doing are Andi, Buffy, Cyrus, Jonah, Amber, TJ, Walker, . The last 8 songs I listened to were “Started” by Iggy Azelea, “Truth Hurts” by Lizzo, “Old Town Road (Remix)” by Lil Nas X & Billy Ray Cyrus, “ME!” by Taylor Swift & P!ATD, “Earth” by Lil Dicky, “7 Rings” by Ariana Grande, and “JESUS RISES (EASTER SONG)” by Trisha Paytas. I will also pick a lyric from the song to represent them.

Andi-”But one of these things is not like the other, like a rainbow with all the colors.”-ME! by Taylor Swift ft. Brendon Urie I chose this lyric because Andi loves painting so like “colors”. But also it’s Taylor Swift, and they both have lots of boy drama.

Buffy-”I just took a DNA test and turns out I’m a 100% that bitch”-Truth Hurts by Lizzo Do I really need to explain? Like Buffy 100% “That Bitch”.

Cyrus-Jesus Rises by Trisha Paytas I dunno. I bet he watches Trisha Paytas.

Jonah-”I’m like the Marlboro Man so I kick on back!”-Old Town Road by Lil Nas X & Billy Ray Ellish Jonah is really laidback and uniro9nically likes this song.

Amber-”I want it, I got it.”-7 Rings by Ariana Grande Amber might not be mean anymore, but she’s always getting when she wants.

TJ-”I Started from the bottom and now I’m rich.”-Started by Iggy Azelea Ignore the fact this is a Sugar Daddy anthum, and just think about it’s a Hip Hop song about becoming the top of the best, which is totally what TJ would listen to. 

Walker-”We love the Earth”-Earth by Lil Dicky Walker would totally be in love with the songs enviormental message.


If you liked this than don’t forget to Like, Comment, Reblog and Follow me, and also look up ANDI MACK TOONS on Youtube and Andi Mack Central on Twitter! If this gets 100 total notes I’ll do the adults!

summary:
@cyrusgoodboye Happy (really late) Birthday Emma💖💖 
[Before I start going off about really sappy friendship stuff I just want to...
body:
@cyrusgoodboye Happy (really late) Birthday Emma💖💖

[Before I start going off about really sappy friendship stuff I just want to apologize in advance for me-not-knowing-how-to-put-my-feelings-into-words]

Y’know if anyone had told me last year that my first friend in the Andi Mack fandom was going to be a Tyrus Shipper who shares views opposite to mine, I would have never believed it. Yet, here we are. And it’s also ironic that I’m saying all of this almost a year to when we first started talking. We became friends in a quite unlikely circumstance but I’m so glad that it happened. Who would’ve guessed a friendship would have come out of me sending a random anon to someone on tumblr? It’s so strange to think about, yet, I’m guessing thats why people say “everything happens for a reason”. So without that one night when I was staying up late crying, none of the major events following would have ever happened. Who knows where I would’ve been now.

Emma, for the past eleven months, you have helped me through so many tough times i don’t know how to express how thankful I am. You’ve given me such good advice on how to cope with my issues I’m forever grateful. Not only have you comforted me when I’m feeling upset, you’ve always made me smile and laugh no matter the circumstances. Seriously, you never believe me when I tell you how sweet you are lmao. From literally giving me your old email so I could make an ao3 to complimenting my art 24/7, you’re truly one of the kindest people I’ve ever met. You have made such a large impact on my life and have taught me so many new things I didn’t know before. (Like teaching me how to use emojis ironically and basically everything else in the twitter language) Emma, legit you’re such an intelligent and talented person I hope you become a famous writer one day because no joke your fanfics have some of the best writing I’ve ever seen. Anyway, to sum up, I never would have thought you would be my friend but I’m so sincerely glad that you are, I wouldn’t have changed anything that happened in the past. I hope you had a good birthday Emma, I love you dude✌️♥️ Sincerely, your Jyrus Friend™️ aka Anon-From-Before aka Hailey :’)

body: Listen, Emily and Luke look great in that photoshoot, but I can’t be the only person who sees the irony in a company called “You’re So Beautiful Now” editing the hell out of their photos to the point where they barely even look like real people anymore.
